  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Desktop PoE Switch",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UniFi Switch 8 PoE is a compact, Layer 2 managed Ethernet switch designed for small offices, retail spaces, classrooms, and home business networks that require Power over Ethernet in a quiet, space-efficient form factor... The fanless cooling design ensures completely silent operation..."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Gigabit Performance",
      "text": "Despite its compact size, the UniFi Switch 8 PoE delivers strong Layer 2 performance suitable for modern Gigabit networks. It provides a switching capacity of 16 Gbps... The switch supports up to 1,000 VLANs, enabling logical network segmentation..."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Centralized Management",
      "text": "The UniFi Switch 8 PoE is managed through the UniFi Network application (version 7.2.94 or later), providing centralized configuration, monitoring, and control via Ethernet. The intuitive UniFi interface allows administrators to deploy and manage the switch alongside other UniFi devices from a single dashboard..."
    }
